text: Tamil Nadu SSLC 10th Result 2024 at dge.tn.gov.in, tnresults.nic.in Live Updates: The Directorate of Government Examinations, Tamil Nadu will declare the TN Class 10th public exam result 2024 today, May 10. Students who appeared in the TN 10th public exam 2024 can access and check the result by visiting the official website- tnresults.nic.in. The necessary required credentials such as the registration number and date of birth are required to download the Tamil Nadu SSLC 10th result 2024. To check the TN 10th result 2024 online students first need to go to the Tamil Nadu board result website. Then on the homepage click on the TN SSLC 2024 result link after which a login window will appear on the screen. Then enter the credentials as required in the specified fields and submit. Once done the Tamil Nadu SSLC result 2024 marksheet will be displayed on the screen. Take the printout of the result mark sheet PDF. TN Tamil Nadu SSLC 10th Result 2024 Highlights Exam Conducting Authority Directorate of Government Examinations, Tamil Nadu Exam Name TN SSLC Exams 2024 Result Name Tamil Nadu 10th Results 2024 TN Class 10th Result 2024 Date May 10, 2024 TN Class 10th Result 2024 Time 9:30 AM TN Board Class 10th Result 2024 Websites tnresults.nic.in dge.tn.gov.in To pass the Tamil Nadu board Class 10 exam 2024 students need to get at least 33 per cent marks in each subject and in aggregate.
